title: Music Label 2008 v.14.0.2.1801
description:
Are you a DJ or a home-user looking for the most efficient way to catalog your music collection? Look no further... Music Label 2008 is the answer to your problems.

Since its initial release in 1994, Music Label lets you catalog your music collection(s) with ease. With powerful CDDB2 support, there is no need to manually type in data... Simply insert the CD and Music Label will do the rest. It can also scan your drives for digital music files.
